🍉 It’s a COCOMELON GIVEAWAY! 🍉 

We’ve teamed up with some of our favorite CoComelon kiddo brands to give three (3) lucky winners the chance to win an amazing prize pack for your @cocomelon_official super fan! 🙌 ✨ 

⭐️ Prizes ($200 value!) ⭐️
@sproutfoods $100 Digital Gift Card
@maryruthorganics Choice of Three (3) CoComelon Liquid Vitamin/Supplements
@rascalandfriends 1 Month Supply of CoComelon Diapers/Training Pants

⭐️ How to Enter ⭐️
1️⃣ Follow all brands: @sproutfoods @maryruthorganics @rascalandfriends
2️⃣ Like AND save this post!
3️⃣ Comment tagging a parent (or more!) that needs to know! Every separate comment with a new tag will count as an additional entry.

🔷 Bonus Entry! 🔷 
Share this post to stories tagging all brands 👍 

Entry period begins 2/5/24 at 7AM PST and closes on 2/12/24 at 11:59PM PST. Three (3) winners will be selected at random on Tuesday 2/13/24, contacted only by the @sproutfoods official account via DM, and announced in stories (please be wary of spam accounts!). If the selected winner(s) do not qualify or respond to claim their prize within 24 hours, we will move on to the next runner up. Good luck! 🤞

⭐️ Terms & Conditions ⭐️
No purchase necessary to enter. This contest is open to US RESIDENTS ONLY that are 18+ and is not associated with Meta. Prizes must be accepted as awarded; no cash substitutes.

🎥: @samanthaneste 💚
